      • tokenize

        java.util.List<Morpheme> tokenize(Tokenizer.SplitMode mode,
                                  java.lang.String text)
        Tokenize a text. This method tokenizes a input text as a sentence. When the text is long, it required a lot of memory.
        パラメータ:
        mode - a mode of splitting
        text - input text
        戻り値:
        a result of tokenizing

      • tokenize

        default java.util.List<Morpheme> tokenize(java.lang.String text)
        Tokenize a text. Tokenize a text with Tokenizer.SplitMode.C.
        パラメータ:
        text - input text
        戻り値:
        a result of tokenizing
        関連項目:
        tokenize(SplitMode,String)
